{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And maybe a half an hour later or an hour later when I felt the potatoes are baked, I took a dash to the place, and I pulled out a potatoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came, and I fed my mother a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she was very weak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She kept on fainting on me all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow we-- we slept through the night in the forest, just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no other voice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If there was anybody that survived, we never knew about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we decided the-- the-- on the next day that we will return to the same forest where that mechanic, my father's worker, used to live because we just didn't know what else to do.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a long way to walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took us a whole day to-- to-- to walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your mother walked?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother kept on fainting all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I propped her up and-- and on the way, I got some milk for her from some farmers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we were coming, some farmers told us that two little girls passed through here the-- the other day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them said her name was-- was Golub.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Ukranians-- they cannot pronounce the G, so they say, 'Hol,' like a H.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they said, the girl, she was-- she said she was 'Holub's' daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I knew my little sister was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to my big surprise, when I arrived to the location where we were going-- where-- where our friend used to live, I found my-- my little sister.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And God knows how she ever managed-- a little girl-- to find a way from such a distance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
